  "url": "https://www.ada.lk/breaking_news/\u0d89\u0daf\u0dd2\u0dbb\u0dd2-\u0daf\u0dd2\u0db1-\u0d9a\u0dd2\u0dc4\u0dd2\u0db4\u0dba\u0dda\u0daf\u0dd3-\u0d89\u0db1\u0dca\u0db0\u0db1-\u0db4\u0ddd\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0db8\u0dca-\u0d85\u0da9\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0dda\u0dc0\u0dd2/11-395636",
  "time_ut": 1658425201,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0d89\u0daf\u0dd2\u0dbb\u0dd2 \u0daf\u0dd2\u0db1 \u0d9a\u0dd2\u0dc4\u0dd2\u0db4\u0dba\u0dda\u0daf\u0dd3 \u0d89\u0db1\u0dca\u0db0\u0db1 \u0db4\u0ddd\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0db8\u0dca \u0d85\u0da9\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0dda\u0dc0\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The fuel queues will reduce in the next few days",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Minister of Electricity and Energy Mr. Kanchana Wijesekera says that when the system of issuing fuel according to the last digit of the vehicle number plate as well as the QR code system is successful, the existing fuel queues will be reduced in the next few days.",
        "He said that after initial technical issues, the FuelPass QR system was successfully tested today and will continue as a pilot project in the next few days before being rolled out across the country from next week.",
        "He says that he would like to express his thanks to all the parties who supported the implementation of this system and that some parties did not join this system.",
        "However, he mentioned that this system will be implemented all over the island in the future."
      ],
